            <title>[CASSANDRA-17118] coordinator_large_read should be actually  coordinator_read_size in cassandra.yaml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17118</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;coordinator_large_read should be actually called coordinator_read_size in cassandra.yaml&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After refactoring the name was changed in the test config but not in the default file.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The issue was not caught because&#160;track_warnings is currently disabled and commented out.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
